      "title": "LP gas gazetted as \u201cspecified goods\u201d",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A Gazette Extraordinary has been issued prescribing liquefied petroleum (LP) gas as \u201cspecified goods\u201d under Section 18 of the Consumer Affairs Authority Act, No. 09 0f 2003 (Amended).",
        "The communiqu\u00e9 was published by the Minister of Trade, Commerce and Food Security Nalin Fernando, taking into account the fact that LP gas is essential to the life of the community."
